Mokgahlo wa '''United''' '''Women’s Organisation (UWO''') o ile wa thakgolwa ka Moranang 1981 ke baemedi ba 400 ba kua Kapa Bophirima. Ba bangwe ba basadi ba ba ilego ba bapala karolo go ba bo maditsela go bulweng ga  mokgahlo o, ba be bana le mafolofolo go Liki ya Basadi Ya ANC ka bo-1950. Mohlala, Dorothy Zihlangu, Mildred Lesia le Dora Tamana e ne e le maloko a ANC. Tamana yo a bego a le mengwageng ye 80 ka nako eo a bego a dutse setulong sa batho ba ba tshephegileng o ile a bula setlhopha se a ileng  a tlhotleletsa basadi botlhe go kopana. UWO ke yona e ilego ya tseya karolo ge merafe  e dutse, e be e kgetholola batho go ya ka semerafe. Ene ya amogela batho ba basweu ka gare ga le kgotlha la yona. Sekao, Amy Thornton mosadi o mosweu o a neng a le leloko la Congress of Democrats (COD) yo a bego a thibetswe go dira ka gare ga dipolotiki  lebakeng la 1959 le 1973 o ile a theeletsa ge a mengwa go tsenela UWO ke Oscar Mphetha.

Mokgahlo o o thomile morago ga kgalefo ya mmusho wa kgatelelo, kgwekgwe-kgolo e le go kopanya basadi kamoka go-lwantsha kgethololo sechabeng, go  boiphedišo le ka gare ga dipolotiki, ga basadi. UWO e be e e-na le kantorokgolo e tee, le makala dikarolong tse fapa-fapanego. Makala ka moka a be a tšeya molao le tshipidiso ya mananeo a le kgotla, le a basadi gotswa go kantorokgolo. 

UWO e ile ya thoma mogwanto wa dipeese ka 1984 le mogwanto kgahlanong le mapaka-a marotho ka 1985. 
Kamorago ga go dira kgerano le UDF, baetapele bjalo ka Cherly Carolus ba ile ba di gogela-pele. Ka di 22 Hlakola 1986 UWO e ile ya tsenela kgwerano le lekheishene la Women's Front. Dileteng tša go swana le Natal go be gona le na kgotla a go swana le 
Natal Women’s Organisation (NOW) and  ka bokoni bophirima gona le Federation of Transvaal Women (FEDTRAW) e lego makgotla a basadi a phagamego. 




